lass=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而且好似好多連登巴打都鐘意郊野公園行山咁<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">郊野起樓? 不了</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n再加上政府打算要發展既棕地都係位於當年既新界東北發展計劃範圍內, 而其他棕地又零交通又分散又深山咁, <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">發展棕地? 不了</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n粉嶺高爾夫球場起黎咪又係變豪宅, 加上地段太近火車站同古洞發展區, 最後咪益左班地產商<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">發展高爾夫球場土地? 不了</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://landforhongkong.hk/tc/img/brownfield_03.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Flandforhongkong.hk%2Ftc%2Fimg%2Fbrownfield_03.png&h=7ca1f7f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">總而言之, 我唔介意等多三十年時間黎cut 150人, 一定要搞掂左之後先好開始諗填海/發展新市镇, 大家同唔同意? <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n講得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌你啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br />\n利申: 月入22k 窮撚, 目標月入85%以上用黎儲錢買樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> , 父母有兩個物業係市區收租用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T07:51:00.000Z","msg":"投你老母"},{"pid":"9b9b1e1dda28ac75032f4c92309f9bc6bf131637","tid":764520,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b9c8907bdf71fc5c04fead99d54c6c0dde593a62","tid":764520,"uid":36478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4c0320ec3e49ed7d2e8266dccbccb7f0837d720a","tid":764520,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T04:47:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">土地供應專責小組問卷link</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://landforhongkong.hk/tc/index.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fl